<ul>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/RobotnikAutomation/summit_x_sim">summit_x_sim</a>: Packages used for the simulation of the SUMMIT-X.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/RobotnikAutomation/summit_x_common">summit_x_common</a>: Contains the URDF description of the SUMMIT-X, platform messages and other files for simulation.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/RobotnikAutomation/summit_x_robot">summit_x_robot</a>: Packages used for the configuration and bringup of the SUMMIT-X robot.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

